{
  "name": "Line + cart discounts (the canonical example)",
  "description": "Modelled on the official guide example. A 5% line discount on Pizza plus a 10% cart-level discount, distributed across lines. The cartridge should apply each line's `totalCartLineItemDiscountAmount` as an AmountDiscount so the basket total lands on `adjustedCartAmount`.",
  "request": {
    "body": {
      "cart": {
        "cartDetails": [
          {
            "cartHeaderId__std": "<sfcc-basket-uuid>",
            "currencyISOCode": "USD",
            "membershipNumber": "MEM-100001",
            "transactionAmount": 110,
            "cartLineDetails": [
              { "cartLineItemId": "abcd1", "cartLineProductId": "01t...PIZZA", "cartLineItemQuantity": 2, "cartLineItemAmount": 100, "cartLineNetUnitPrice__std": 50 },
              { "cartLineItemId": "abcd2", "cartLineProductId": "01t...BURGER", "cartLineItemQuantity": 2, "cartLineItemAmount": 10, "cartLineNetUnitPrice__std": 5 }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "response": {
    "status": 200,
    "body": {
      "cart": {
        "cartDetails": [
          {
            "cartHeaderId": "<sfcc-basket-uuid>",
            "initialCartAmount": 110,
            "adjustedCartAmount": 69.5,
            "totalDiscountAmount": 40.5,
            "totalCartLevelDiscountAmount": 30,
            "totalLineLevelDiscountAmount": 10.5,
            "appliedCartPromotionDetails": [
              {
                "promotionId": "0c8xx00000005R7AAI",
                "displayName": "10% off on Cart",
                "cartAmountBeforeDiscount": 99.5,
                "cartAmountAfterDiscount": 89.5,
                "cartLevelDiscountAmount": 10,
                "isAutomatic": true,
                "nonPricingRewards": {}
              }
            ],
            "cartLineDetails": [
              {
                "cartLineItemId": "abcd1",
                "cartLineProduct": "Pizza",
                "cartLineItemQuantity": 2,
                "cartLineItemAmountBeforeDiscount": 100,
                "cartLineItemAmountAfterDiscount": 66.36,
                "totalCartLineItemDiscountAmount": 33.64,
                "totalCartLinePromotionsDiscountAmount": 5,
                "totalCartPromotionsDistributedDiscountAmount": 28.64,
                "appliedCartLinePromotionDetails": [
                  {
                    "promotionId": "0c8xx00000005NtAAI",
                    "displayName": "5% off on Pizza",
                    "cartLineItemAmountBeforeDiscount": 100,
                    "cartLineItemAmountAfterDiscount": 95,
                    "cartLineItemDiscountAmount": 5,
                    "couponCode": "PIZZA5",
                    "currencyIsoCode": "USD",
                    "isAutomatic": false
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "cartLineItemId": "abcd2",
                "cartLineProduct": "Burger",
                "cartLineItemQuantity": 2,
                "cartLineItemAmountBeforeDiscount": 10,
                "cartLineItemAmountAfterDiscount": 3.14,
                "totalCartLineItemDiscountAmount": 6.86,
                "totalCartLinePromotionsDiscountAmount": 5.5,
                "totalCartPromotionsDistributedDiscountAmount": 1.36,
                "appliedCartLinePromotionDetails": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "notes": "Per-line totalCartLineItemDiscountAmount already includes the line's share of cart-level discounts (5 + 28.64 = 33.64). Summing the line totals (33.64 + 6.86 = 40.5) equals totalDiscountAmount, so applying them per line — and NOT the cart-level discount separately — makes the basket total equal adjustedCartAmount (69.5) with no double-counting. The cartLineItemId values must echo the ids the cartridge sent (it sends the SFCC line-item UUID)."
}
